## Critical Notes
- NEVER skip rule validation
- ALWAYS document rule application
- NEVER ignore rule conflicts
- ALWAYS track deviations
- NEVER bypass critical rules
- ALWAYS update documentation
- NEVER assume rule compliance
- ALWAYS verify rule effectiveness

